  ('optician-moex-01931', 'optician', 'optician-moex-108-148c1cdf', 'sub-optician-04', NULL, 'single_choice', '受檢者雙眼遠方矯正度數為OD-4.00 DS/OS-5.00 DS，在執行正負相對調節（NRA/PRA）的檢查時，綜合 驗光儀上分別轉到OD-3.00 DS/OS-4.00 DS及OD-7.00 DS/OS-8.00 DS時，受檢者表示視標會出現持續性 模糊，則檢查結果應如何記錄？', '["NRA/PRA：+1.00/-3.00", "NRA/PRA：+4.00/-4.00", "NRA/PRA：-4.00/+4.00", "NRA/PRA：-3.00/+2.00"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:35+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "b5729e769b59", "answer_pdf_sha1": "e88e08bae45b", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "108060", "c": "402", "s": "0807", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "驗光學概要", "year": "108", "exam_name": "108年專技人員高等考試大地工程技師考試分階段考試、驗船師、引水人、第一次食品技師考試、高等暨普通考試消防設備人員考試、普通考試地政士、專責...", "original_question_number": 12, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optician", "db_exam_id": "optician"}'::jsonb, NULL),
